{"tid":1151281,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"白底想曬黑，曬黑返少少又點keep","createTime":"2019-05-12T12:41:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-13T13:08:48.000Z","uid":231742,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"71ea406171f870ada760c413372bd2d9a1cb3a94","tid":1151281,"uid":231742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T12:41:10.000Z","msg":"我皮膚白底<br />\n唔鐘意咁<br />\n唔想做一個白雪雪既麻甩佬<br />\n感覺好gay<br />\n每年夏天都好把握機會去曬太陽曬黑啲<br />\n但係咁<br />\n太陽伯伯係好鐘意同我玩遊戲<br />\n返工星期一至五office hour個陣<br />\n佢老尾個太陽就曬到行一行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好啦到左星期六日放假想去曬下太陽啦<br />\n佢老尾個太陽就縮到行一行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要落埋雨乜鳩outdoor活動都做唔到<br />\n到星期一朝早個陣<br />\n又好好天曬足星期一至五<br />\n我灰到盡頭...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以尋日朝早難得我見咁好天<br />\n即刻狗衝去曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知一曬就曬過龍..<br />\n心諗想曬耐少少黑多少少都好<br />\n最後曬紅左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n曬紅左個啲位到而家仲好撚熱<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除左下世投胎做黑人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今世係白皮膚既我<br />\n可以點解決呢個問題呢<br />\n請指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eae2cb51dcd45f145bf1164404ef8c5fc520170","tid":1151281,"uid":231742,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T12:43:57.000Z","msg":"紅到咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6kSBNQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6kSBNQQ.png&h=2b1a6f95&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gYF7UvR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgYF7UvR.png&h=5aa4ebd1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ecf57530446053f2c267290e3ae143cccf42f5bf","tid":1151281,"uid":28818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T12:45:36.000Z","msg":"曬傷左 樓主準備有排受<br />\n痛撚到仆街 等佢甩皮再生返先叫好d<br />\n起碼痛半個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmo